<div class='welcome' style='text-align: center'>Welcome to the Makers Rock, Paper, Scissors Game</div>
<div class='register' style='text-align: center'><a href='/register'>register</a></div>
<div class='login' style='text-align: center'><a href='/login'>log in</a></div>
<div class='end_game' style='text-align: center'><a href='/end_game'>log out</a></div>
